quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  26,10,"And when your Lord called out to Moses, that, \"Go to the unjust people"
  26,11,people of Pharaoh. Will they not guard (against evil)
  26,12,"He said, \"My Lord! I fear that they will deny me"
  26,13,"further, my bosom straitens and my language is not fluent, so send for Aaron (to help me)"
  26,14,And they have (the charge of) a crime against me so I fear that they will kill me
  26,15,"He said, \"By no means, so both of you go with Our signs, We are with you, Hearing"
  26,16,"So go to Pharaoh then say: We are sent (by) the Lord of the worlds (with a message)"
  26,17,that you should send the children of Israel with us
  26,18,"He (Pharaoh) said, \"Were you not fostered among us as a child? And you did stay among us for many years of your life"
  26,19,and you did that deed of yours which you did and you are of the ungrateful ones
  26,20,"He said, \"I did it then, when I was of those in error"
  26,21,"so I fled from you when I feared you, but my Lord granted me wisdom and made me one of the messengers"
  26,22,Now (should) that favour with which you favoured me (become the cause) for your enslaving the children of Isreal?”
  26,23,"Pharaoh said, \"And who is the Lord of the worlds"
  26,24,"He said, \"The Lord of the skies and the earth and that which is between them, if you (want) to be of those who are certain"
  26,25,"He said to those around him, \"Do you not hear"
  26,26,"He said, \"Your Lord and the Lord of your ancient fathers"
  26,27,"He said, \"Your messenger who has been sent to you is certainly possessed by jinn"
  26,28,"He said, \"Lord of the east and the west and that which is between them, if you have sense"
  26,29,"He said, \"If you take a god other than me I will definitely place you among the prisoners"
  26,30,"He said, \"Even if I bring to you something as a clear proof"
  26,31,"He said, \"Then bring it, if you are of the truthful ones"
  26,32,So he threw down his staff when it became a clear serpent
  26,33,and he drew out his hand when it became white for those who were seeing